#: ../../source/system/power.rst:34 4f252a5c05d549a9946ed9426219c9fe
msgid "Set power output of the external ports."
msgstr "设置外部端口的电源输出。"

#: ../../source/system/power.rst:36 0bffd59d48e1456f807a638a759c0118
msgid ""
"When ``enable`` is True, the power output of the external ports is in "
"output mode. When ``enable`` is False, the power output of the external "
"ports is in input mode."
msgstr ""
"当 ``enable`` 为 True 时，外部端口的电源输出为输出模式。当 ``enable`` 为 False "
"时，外部端口的电源输出为输入模式。"

#: ../../source/system/power.rst:40 4b244d41c0b440859bfc6014f70d3c02
msgid ""
"``port`` is the port number, optional values are available in :ref:`class"
" PORT`, only valid for M5Stack Station."
msgstr "``port`` 是端口号，可选值见 :ref:`class PORT`，仅对 M5Stack Station 有效。"

